Class PhotographBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • gallery.beans.AbstractBean<Photograph>
      • gallery.beans.PhotographBean

  • @Path(value="/photographs")
public class PhotographBean
extends AbstractBean<Photograph>
    Photograph Enterprise Java Bean, maps to a Photograph Hibernate Entity. Also a REST service mapping to /YourPersonalPhotographOrganiser/resources/photographs.
